						<summary>

						<p>On a broken slab leaning against the front wall of the Rāmēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 12th century.</p>						

						<p>It seems to register a gift of land which was entrusted into the hands of Amṛitarāśipaṇḍita. The earlier part of the inscription is lost.</p>						

						</summary>
